data.description: **Seller will pay up to $8,000 towards a BUYER'S RATE BUY DOWN fee with acceptable offer!** GREAT Location near Woodfin Ridge Golf Club and Lake Bowen! Welcome to this charming home close to the growing area of upper Boiling Springs and downtown Inman in a limited home site community, with quick access to both I-26 & I-85 that will let you get anywhere in the upstate with ease. This spacious 4-bedroom, 3 1/2-bathroom home offers comfortable living with an open floor plan and plenty of natural light, equipped as a Smart home. Entertain guests in the lovely formal dining room off the front entrance complete with Butler's Pantry. The beautiful up-to-date kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large island, perfect for entertaining. Sip your morning coffee beside the 2 large windows in the breakfast space. Relax in the cozy great room with a gas fireplace and high ceilings, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The Main floor master suite features a walk-in closet and a private ensuite with dual vanities, and a separate shower. Upstairs you'll find 3 well-appointed bedrooms with plenty of closet space for storage, a large flexible bonus space/den and two full baths! This home boasts ample amounts of extra storage with a walk-in attic space, coat closet in the entry, large broom closet in laundry room, 2 linen closets, and a butler's pantry. Step outside to your own backyard oasis, complete with patio, landscaped fire pit and a fenced-in yard, ideal for outdoor gatherings and playtime. This home is move-in ready, so you can start enjoying all it has to offer right away! Don't miss out on this great value in Boiling Springs. It's the perfect place to call home! Contact us today to schedule a showing and make this lovely property your new home!
